# ---------------------------------------------------------------------
# Privacy lock-in — CSI project data.
# The public site carries methodology and aggregate results only. Raw
# captures, device identifiers, and spatial/floor-plan data must never
# be committed. See README "Privacy" section before adding any CSI
# asset to this repo — when in doubt, keep it out of git.
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------

# Catch-all: anything placed in these directories is never committed,
# regardless of file type.
/private/
/raw-data/
/captures/
/sessions/

# Raw CSI capture formats and session data.
*.pcap
*.pcapng
*.csi
*.iq
session_*.csv
*_session.csv
*.sqlite
*.sqlite3

# Device / network identifiers (MACs, SSIDs, node identity dumps).
*device-fingerprints*
*mac-address*
*mac-table*
*ssid-list*
nvs_identity*

# Floor plans / apartment maps / spatial-mapping outputs.
*floorplan*
*floor-plan*
*apartment-map*
*spatial-map*
*zone-map*
*.dxf
